{"tid":1997140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[又係時候推舊Post] 支那人唔會教你的鴉片戰爭真相","createTime":"2020-05-01T12:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T13:14:26.000Z","uid":119393,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"50ae271a4c439bb6cfc6d7853741c0c3b1bd7589","tid":1997140,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:34:01.000Z","msg":"1. 林則徐鴉片戰爭後稱&quot;所恨者，內地之民嗜洋煙而不嗜土煙&quot;<br />\n2. 1870年代中國鴉片消費已基本上自給自足, 1880年代首次出口, 1900年代國產鴉片佔全世界產量九成<br />\n3. 中國沿海各省軍費, 以至洋務運動基本上都係靠種植鴉片收入支撐<br />\n4. 中國向全世界出口鴉片獲得鉅利, 單係美國一年輸入數十萬磅<br />\n5. 國產鴉片一開始目標客戶係海外華人移民, 苦力, 及後向其他亞洲移民擴散, 最後更向當地白人藍領埋手, 各地政府禁之不絕, 直接導致《排華法案》<br />\n6. 於上海舉行萬國禁煙會及《海牙鴉片公約》的產生唔係一般支那人諗既因為清朝被中華民國推翻, 中國人站起來以鴉片受害國身份主辦; 而係美國在美西戰爭後從西班牙獲得菲律賓, 菲律賓主教受不了中國產鴉片對菲律賓華人的毒害向美國總統要求!!"},{"pid":"f2720fd1081c07b312d14ab17dad72461bffca33","tid":1997140,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c65b323ab73af0e8b4d5f62b46a9dbc658ce3a","tid":1997140,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:40:20.000Z","msg":"等緊一問我&quot;source?&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ee2e63491476aa0a125be7d3997f95571cb05c","tid":1997140,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81c65b323ab73af0e8b4d5f62b46a9dbc658ce3a","tid":1997140,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:40:20.000Z","msg":"等緊一問我&quot;source?&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:13:48.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"7a297c4bf0a74859b098ffb347a1d22a939a97ad","tid":1997140,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:14:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zbuRXqPI4l0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzbuRXqPI4l0&d=29ui5Tvv6a